<style>
p {
  color: red;
  --a: var(--a, red);
  color: var(--a, grcam@mcc.id.au">
<link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables-1/#cycles">
<link rel="match" href="support/color-green-ref.html">
<style>
p {
  color: red;
  --a: var(--a, red);
  color: var(--a, green);
}
</style>
<p>This text must be green.</p>
